## Git Workflow

Conventional commits enforced via [commitizen](https://commitizen-tools.github.io/commitizen/):

```
<type>(<scope>): <subject>
```

Types: `feat`, `fix`, `docs`, `style`, `refactor`, `test`, `chore`

Git hooks run automatically via hk on commit and push.
